automate sawS.cutoff
  8000 R:80 11000:4@smooth R:28 8000:4@smooth R:36 11000:4@smooth R:28 9000:4@smooth R:28
automate sawS.glide
  2.5 R:176 5:12@lin R:36

automate sawA.gain
  1.8 R:80 1.45:1 R:31 1.8:1 R:39 1.45:1 R:31 1.8:1 R:19 1.5:1 R:19.6
automate sawA.pan
  0.35
automate sawA.detune
