automate sawA.cutoff
  6500 R:80 9000:4@smooth R:28 6500:4@smooth R:36 9000:4@smooth R:28 7500:4@smooth R:28
automate sawA.glide
  3.5 R:176 5:12@lin R:36

automate sawT.gain
  1.8 R:80 1.45:1 R:31 1.8:1 R:39 1.45:1 R:31 1.8:1 R:19 1.5:1 R:19.6
